item.title: Gravitrax-compatible-battery-case
item.description:
Gravitrax-compatibles Batteriefach

Für Motoren wird Energie benötigt.
Hier ein Batteriefach für 2x AA.

Die Batteriefedern sind aus kleinen Taschenlampen übrig geblieben. Gibt es aber auch bei Ali.
Etwas Löten wird benötigt.

Bitte klebe den Ring auf der Unterseite ein. Er wird bei vielen Gravitrax-kompatiblen Designs verwendet.
(z.B. von Hubert76 / https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4721294 )



Gravitrax-compatible battery case
You need energy for an engine.
Here is a battery-case for 2x AA.
The battery contacts were from unused battery lamps. But you can get these also from Ali.
You have to solder something.

Use the ring to glue it in at the bottom. You can find here at many gravitrax compatible things. (i.e. from Hubert76 / https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4721294 )

Note: I am in no way associated with Ravensburger or Gravitrax, this is just a design that is compatible with the Gravitrax system that provides functionality the stock parts do not. I do this just for mere fun.

item.title: Glueing Support for Titanfall Helmet
item.description:
These are two printed gluing supports for Kykel's excellent Titanfall helmet.

The first is to strengthen the joint between the crown and skullcap which is does not have a lot of gluing area.
The second is for a central split on the skullcap which I did to fit it on my printer. The skullcap is very thin and this just strengthens everything.

They are not perfect and I did have to trim the support between the skullcap and the crown to get it to fit around the crown piece properly.

Finally, Kykel does plan to address these issues so they may not be needed in future.

item.title: Gravitrax-compatible-round-elevator
item.description:
Gravitrax-compatibler Scheiben-Lift

Um die Kugel stets in Bewegung zu halten braucht es Energie.
Hier eine kleine Variante, die einige Zentimeter hebt, aber einen relativ großen Durchsatz hat.

  • Das Design ist ohne Blockierung. Mehrere Kugel können warten und werden nacheinander transportiert.
  • Für den Druck wird kein Support benötigt.
  • Für das Transportrad bitte hohe Druckqualität verwenden.

Es wird ein N20-Motor mit Schneckengetriebe benutzt.

Motor: N20 Gear Motor (https://de.aliexpress.com/item/10000008795281.html)
Bitte langsame Variante verwenden (4-17rpm, single shaft).

Bitte klebe den Ring auf der Unterseite ein. Er wird bei vielen Gravitrax-kompatiblen Designs verwendet.
(z.B. von Hubert76 / https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4721294 )



Gravitrax-compatible round elevator
For Gravitrax you need evertime fresh energy. Here is a small design, what bring you some centimeter, but with higher throughput.
  • The design is non-blocking. Some marbles can wait and will then be transported.
  • You need no support for printing.
  • Please use high quality for the transport disk!
Here is a gear motor N20 used. Motor: N20 Gear Motor (https://de.aliexpress.com/item/10000008795281.html) Please use slowest type. (4-17rpm, single shaft). Use the ring to glue it in at the bottom. You can find here at many gravitrax compatible things. (i.e. from Hubert76 / https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:4721294 )

Note: I am in no way associated with Ravensburger or Gravitrax, this is just a design that is compatible with the Gravitrax system that provides functionality the stock parts do not. I do this just for mere fun.

item.title: Smith - Selsted tweeter horn for 1" compression drivers
item.description:
This is a design inspired by the Smith Selsted tweeter. The original one was for a 0.5" driver, and these are not that common, so I just tried to make one for a 1" driver. I have not made any measurements yet. I assume it will be usable something like 3 kHz and up. I want to test one with the large multicell. This is in fact also a multicell horn using exponential expansion in the horizontal plane and diffraction in the vertical plane.

Print with the flange flat on the bed, the version with vanes may benefit from using supports.
